“Bonjour, my name is Nonye Anne, a fashion & lifestyle blogger of Thisthingcalledfashionn”, an enthusiastic Anne makes her introduction. Anne is one of the passionate ones who enjoys her job as a digital marketer, fashion consultant, model and content creator. She describes her style as “classy, comfortable & stylish with a touch of edge”. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-579081 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Screenshot3-451x598.png" alt="" width="1000" height="1326" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Screenshot3-451x598.png 451w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Screenshot3-420x557.png 420w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Screenshot3-181x240.png 181w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Screenshot3-362x480.png 362w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Screenshot3-452x600.png 452w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Screenshot3.png 463w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /> The fashion enthusiast does not joke with her ice-cream even when creating and editing fashion videos. To Anne, there is no little or big lie. “I hate little lies, it irritates me when people tell “unnecessary lies” just tell me as it is”. Click to see some of her style pieces below: